## ğŸ”§ Comandos Ãšteis

### Django
```bash
# Executar servidor local
python manage.py runserver

# Criar migraÃ§Ãµes
python manage.py makemigrations

# Aplicar migraÃ§Ãµes
python manage.py migrate

# Criar superusuÃ¡rio
